illegally importing tigers, leopards and mountain lions to their sprawling
ranch -- then charging people to kill them at close range and take their skins
home as trophies.;    Floyd Lester Patterson III, Dawn Patterson and Kenneth
Oravsky, all of Lockwood, face 38 criminal charges connected with the big game
